      • main

        public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
        Inside the main() method we are creating 4 objects of type SalesRepresentative which we are then including in an array of the same type. We are printing on the console the content of the newly created array reps. We create an instance of type Ranking called sorter on which we call the bubbleSort() and the showResult() methods. On the console we can see the contents of the reps array printed in descending order based on revenue figure..
